crazy red: Privacy policy

Welcome to the crazy red game for Android!

the game is available on Google Play.

The game does not require any user registration. The game does not require the user to provide any personal information.

I have not programmed this game to collect any personally identifiable information. All data (game preferences (like level, score, etc.) created by the you is stored on your device only, and can be simply erased by clearing the game's data or uninstalling it.

If you find any security vulnerability that has been inadvertently caused by me, or have any question regarding how the game protectes your privacy, please send me an email and I will surely try to fix it/help you.

Yours sincerely,
Red-A games studio

